Interface jtelos.PropositionOrPrimitive

public interface PropositionOrPrimitive
extends NamedObject
This interface is used to represent both Propositions and Primitives in Telos. In particular, the to method for a Proposition returns a reference to an object implemented from this interface. Indeed, the to field of a Telos proposition can either be another Telos proposition or a primitive literal (i.e., either a String, an integer or a floating point value).

See Also:
